#note: The restoration follows Lambert’s. It is inspired by the lexical list @i{Malku} I 99.
3'. !zz [... !bs ra]-ba#-an-nu !cm : {lu₂}ha-za-nu : !zz x# [...]
#lem: u; +rabiānum[mayor]N$rabannu; hazannu[mayor]N; u; u

4'. !zz [... !bs KI !cm : er]-ṣe#-ti₃ : KI : qaq-qar : !zz [...]
