5'. !zz [... !bs nu-ma]-at !cm : u₂-na-a-tu₂ : [...]
#lem: u; +numātu[movable goods]N$numāt; +unūtu[tools]N$unâtu; u

$ single ruling
6'. !zz [ṣa-a]-tu₂# šu-ut KA ša₂ šum-ma# [a-me-lu ...]
#lem: ṣâtu[commentary]N; šūt[those of]DET; pî[mouth]N; ša[of]DET; šumma[if]MOD; amēlu[man]N; u

7'. !zz [IM?] {m?}{d?}AG?#-[...]
#lem: ṭuppi[tablet]N; u

#note: The tentative reading of the name in the colophon follows Frahm @i{GMTR} 5 (2011) p. 242.

